    "name": "Woundwyrm",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Woundwyrms are ferocious predators native to the corrupted landscape of the Worldwound. They are equally at home in sea and sky, above the ground and below it. Oozing deliquescence seeps from between their cracked, rocky scales, and a constant fume of rainbow hues drifts out of their gullets, save when they inhale and ingest the very substance of disintegrating reality."
        }
    ],
